Edit Task data

To edit the Task select the Edit action

    The Task opens in Edit mode. In Edit mode of the Task you can:

    1. Update Task metadata
    2. Add additional sections and text in the Task landing page
    3. Format the free text by using the document formatting controls at the top of the page or add additional widgets to present additional data in the selected tab

    Want more?
